  "2368030": {
    "name": "Delusion Out of Space",
    "steam_appid": 2368030,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你在一艘神秘的宇宙飞船上醒来，周围是一片废墟和混乱。系统正在崩溃，黑暗的走廊隐藏着潜在的危险。然而，最让你感到不安的是脑海中回荡的神秘声音。它呼唤你，促使你深入飞船深处，科学家们曾在那里进行危险的意识实验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >奈亚拉斯的埃沃斯 (Eh’vos) 试图为他的种族释放新的潜力，为此不惜一切代价。然而，事情并没有按照计划进行，他现在已经失去了控制。前方的每一个转角都隐藏着他大胆实验的后果，但你依然继续前进。探索这艘飞船，在关键时刻做出选择，见证你的决定如何塑造你的命运以及身边人们的命运。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >即兴生存</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人类的脆弱性与生物无情力量之间的持续冲突令人紧张不已。生存不仅依赖于你的武器，还需要掌握躲避或抵挡攻击的完美时机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368030/extras/6b574de1d5b1c6f37a14f8b8dac51689.poster.avif?t=1768108669\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368030/extras/6b574de1d5b1c6f37a14f8b8dac51689.webm?t=1768108669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368030/extras/6b574de1d5b1c6f37a14f8b8dac51689.mp4?t=1768108669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >解开奈亚拉斯外星飞船的谜团</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸于要求逻辑与创意的挑战性谜题中，以推进故事发展。尝试各种与飞船设备操作相关的独特迷你游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368030/extras/970668fc185ace3d3520c124b2d5145c.poster.avif?t=1768108669\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368030/extras/970668fc185ace3d3520c124b2d5145c.webm?t=1768108669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368030/extras/970668fc185ace3d3520c124b2d5145c.mp4?t=1768108669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >找到你最喜欢的武器</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用从回收材料制作的多功能武器与敌人对抗，每种武器都有独特功能——精确射击、在过热风险下释放巨大威力，或者让敌人冻结。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368030/extras/d9ea0e9ef20b3b3cd13209a7f4c59883.poster.avif?t=1768108669\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368030/extras/d9ea0e9ef20b3b3cd13209a7f4c59883.webm?t=1768108669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368030/extras/d9ea0e9ef20b3b3cd13209a7f4c59883.mp4?t=1768108669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与环境互动</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这艘飞船是一个活生生的生态系统，每件事物都遵循其指定的功能。 在极端条件下，居民维持其功能。每次与他们的互动都会揭示机会和威胁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368030/extras/fee3dbb5ac1d8439900d225e54c3e9bd.poster.avif?t=1768108669\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368030/extras/fee3dbb5ac1d8439900d225e54c3e9bd.webm?t=1768108669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368030/extras/fee3dbb5ac1d8439900d225e54c3e9bd.mp4?t=1768108669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索飞船的秘密</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现飞船内仍在运作且被严格禁止的区域。准备好穿过技术隧道系统并找到隐藏的路径吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368030/extras/c8d3a96f7619e49542454255e6fbd7c8.poster.avif?t=1768108669\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368030/extras/c8d3a96f7619e49542454255e6fbd7c8.webm?t=1768108669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368030/extras/c8d3a96f7619e49542454255e6fbd7c8.mp4?t=1768108669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
